{"tid":2228679,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警涉胸襲女記者　同袍助鬆人拒絕道歉　受害人：追究到底","createTime":"2020-10-03T18:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T07:02:25.000Z","uid":240362,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"e9ec30ce6fef81f943cce522ebcc8ff83b6cb73d","tid":2228679,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T18:34:09.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】中共建政71周年，豺狼當道。今年10.1警方派出千計警力在銅鑼灣隨意圍捕市民及驅趕記者，一名網媒女記者採訪期間，被一名隸屬機動部隊的男警推撞及觸碰胸部。她即場質問男警，卻在警方傳媒聯絡隊阻攔下讓男警離開。記者所屬媒體譴責警方惡行，表明一定追究到底。<br />\n<br />\n被侵犯女記者嚴小姐為網媒「初媒」記者，昨日接受本報訪問憶述事發情況。當晚約7時，嚴小姐在銅鑼灣記利佐治街附近正在拍攝一名被捕者，警方突然拉起封鎖線阻隔記者。「個時有男警用手推咗我一下，叫我上返行人路，我叫佢唔好掂我」，男警卻進一步挨向她，上身貼向其胸部。嚴當時大聲呼叫，男警不但無理會，更輕佻反問：「我點掂你呀？掂你邊度啫？」傳媒聯絡隊上前了解，但同時拉走男警，男警笑着離開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201004/L3IN7EHERJF7XN52Y63WD34KEM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201004%2FL3IN7EHERJF7XN52Y63WD34KEM%2F&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJduvO%2FPyVe1I8S2KINgfvOuE%3D&h=e4457f6b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201004%2FL3IN7EHERJF7XN52Y63WD34KEM%2F&h=4c437367\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201004/L3IN7EHERJF7XN52Y63WD34KEM/</a>"},{"pid":"ce5720388f1a5169018ef4fb1ff81567f40c50e1","tid":2228679,"uid":240362,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T18:34:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/g3e2UGoEBG9Bi7TaSSfoS-yso7c=/567x748/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QD35Y4CDUVFUXODUS52JHZLPXU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fg3e2UGoEBG9Bi7TaSSfoS-yso7c%3D%2F567x748%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQD35Y4CDUVFUXODUS52JHZLPXU.gif&h=c944ea2a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93dd2a74ea2f1d1cd67159c842414ceb3d78a300","tid":2228679,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,